  <body>
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-spacing:0;outline:none;margin:0;padding:0;border:none;background-color:#ebebeb" bgcolor="#ebebeb">
      <tbody style="border-spacing:0;border:none;outline:none">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background:#fff;border:0; max-width:616px;margin:0px auto;">
              <tbody>
                <tr style="background-color:#466289">
                  <td style="padding:10px">
                    <img src = "<%= root_url %>assets/shared/logo-mobile.png" height="38px" width="109px" alt="Spliddit">
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:10px; color: #000000">
                    <p>Spliddit is live! <a href = "http://spliddit.org/">http://spliddit.org/</a></p>

                    <p>Spliddit is a not-for-profit academic endeavor. Its mission is twofold:</p>

                    <ol>
                      <li>To provide easy access to carefully designed fair division methods, thereby making the world a bit fairer.</li>
                      <li>To communicate to the public the beauty and value of research in computer science, mathematics, and economics, from an unusual perspective.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <p>We appreciate your patience, and thank you for your interest. We are currently in public beta, so we'd appreciate it if you would give the website a try and report any bugs on our <a href = "http://spliddit.org/feedback">feedback page</a>.</p>

                    <p>
                      <center>
                        <%= link_to "spliddit.org", root_url, only_path: false, style: "display: block; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; background: #59df72; border: 0; color: white; -moz-border-radius: 10px; -webkit-border-radius: 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 1.25em; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 1em; max-width: 140px;" %>
                      </center>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      Sincerely,<br>
                      Ariel Procaccia<br>
                      Jonathan Goldman
                    </p>
                    <p><em>Note: You are receiving this message because your email address was entered on our homepage in the preceding months. We won't be sending any further messages to this address. </em></p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
